data.description: GORGEOUS CAPE COD HOME WITH DISTANCE MOUNTAIN VIEWS IN THE PERFECT NORTHEAST GEORGIA COMMUNITY...BEAUTIFULLY landscaped and well-maintained grounds adding all the CHARM! Warm welcoming home providing by the sweetest rocking chair front porch, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the sights and sounds that Panorama Estates has to offer! OPEN concept design featuring SPACIOUS Living room, Kitchen, and Dining area making entertaining a breeze! SUPER functional Kitchen with an abundance of cabinetry, countertop space, peninsula island with additional seating, and walk-in pantry! MASSIVE and COZY Family room featuring stone stacked wall with gas fireplace, plenty of natural lighting, and exterior access to the screened back porch providing the ultimate space for friends and family gatherings! Sunroom makes the perfect office or den PLUS great spot to enjoy the outdoors being in the comfort of your home! Exterior access to the back porch and fenced backyard, ready for furry friends! LARGE Primary bedroom on main level featuring walk-in closets and private access to the full bathroom with tub/shower combination. Two OVER-SIZED guest bedrooms sharing the second full bathroom with tub/shower combination and over-sized vanity! Large, wooded backyard gives feels of a secret garden featuring rock paths, mature trees and plants, outdoor lighting, and fencing! HUGE detached garage with MASSIVE storage room! BONUSES - NEW roof, shutters, carpet in Primary bedroom, front porch steps, resealed the driveway, and NEW sidewalks and patio!!!! FULL house and garage generator!!! Contact our team for your private viewing today!!
